                    <span>Many people know that this book had tremendous impact on the birth of the pattern community.<p>But do you know what this book realy aimed for and what realy happend that made an update to this book an unnecessary  job?<p>Java was born! And Java is doing so great!<p>If you know C++ and  Java very well, you may reach the same conclusion.<p>This book is obsolete  in some perspectives, but it is a classic in C++.</span>
                  
              
